Narrative:
Alia Bhatt and Ranbir Kapoor are all set for their big day as they gear up to tie the knot on April 14 in the presence of their family and close friends.
Ahead of the wedding, media personnel has been gathering around the couple's home and the houses of their family members as well and on Thursday, the much-loved couple's kind gesture towards them has become the talk of the town.
Title: Alia Bhatt and Ranbir Kapoor sent Their Wedding' laddu for Media
